General.Name: Aukett Fitzroy Robinson Group
General.Description: Aukett Swanke Group Plc, together with its subsidiaries, provides integrated professional design services in the United Kingdom and Continental Europe. It offers architectural design services, including master planning, interior design, and fit-out capability; and executive architectural delivery services under the Veretec brand. The company also provides architect of record; master planning and urban design; workplace strategy; and related engineering services. It offers its services to the commercial office, research and education, mixed use hybrid, and hospitality sectors. The company was formerly known as Aukett Fitzroy Robinson Group plc and changed its name to Aukett Swanke Group Plc in March 2014. Aukett Swanke Group Plc was founded in 1906 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
